verses.text: Mamin Jehová, te wach' yic heb' sk'anab'ajan a k'ayb'ub'al, malaj mach tz'alan heb' chukal.
Te wach' yic heb' sk'anab'ajan a kachnab'il, t'a smasanil sk'ol heb' tz'och tzak'an uuj.
Aton heb' max k'ulanlaj chukal, heb' sk'anab'ajan sb'eyb'alan tas tzala'.
Mamin Jehová, a ach ix ala' to tz'akan tz'aj sk'anab'ajax a checnab'il.
Comonoc aynhejoch t'a in k'ool in k'anab'ajan a ley.
¿Tas yuj ol in q'uixwoc tato tzin k'anab'ajej masanil a checnab'il chi'?
Ol wal wach' lolonel t'ayach t'a smasanil in k'ool ayic toxo ix in k'ayb'ej a ley te tojol.
Ol in k'anab'ajej a ley. Manh in actejkan t'a junelnhej. BET
¿Tas wal ol aj heb' kelemtac yic max och smul heb'? Anhej tato sk'anab'ajej a lolonel heb'.
D'a smasanil in k'ol tzin och tzak'an uuj. Manh a cha wik'el in b'ha t'a a checnab'il.
Ix cham wal in k'ayb'an a lolonel yic wach' max och in mul t'ayach.
Mamin Jehová, te wach' ach. k'ayb'ej in t'a a ley.
Ol walel masanil a ley, aton juntzanh alb'ilkan uuj.
Ek'b'al stzalaj in k'ool ayic tzin k'anab'ajan in kachnab'il tzak'a' t'a yichanh pax swik'an masanil makanhil b'eyumal.
Ol in naub'tanhej a checnab'il ix ak' t'ayonh. Ol cham wal in naub'tanhan a k'ayb'ub'al.
Ol wak' tzalajb'oc in k'ool yet' a checnab'il tik, manh ol b'atkan a lolonel satk'olal wuuj. GUÍMEL
Ak' a wach'k'olal t'ayin yic wach' ol in k'anab'ajej a lolonel yacb'an pitzan into.
Jac in sat yic wach' snachajel a k'ayb'ub'al wuuj, aton te satub'tac yochi.
Ek'elb'anhej wek' t'a sat lu'um tik, manh a k'ub'ejel a checnab'il t'ayin.
Snib'ej wal in k'ol swojtaquejel a ley t'a junjun rato.
Ha ach ton tza cach heb' ak'umtac syutej sb'a, aton heb' katab'il yujto syik'el sb'a heb' t'a a checnab'il.
Yujto tzin k'anab'ajej in kachnab'il tzak'a', yuj chi' colinel t'a schukal lolonel heb' tzin patikaneli.
Wach'chom a heb' yajal smol naej heb' in yixtani, a inxo a chekab' in tik, a a ley ol in naub'tanhej.
Swak' tzalaj in k'ool yuj in kachnab'il, yujto syak' in razón. DÁLET
Ijan wal tzin cham swab'i, ak' in k 'inal ichataxon alani.
Ix in ch'ox chajtil in b'ey t'a ichanh, ix in a tak'wani. k'ayb'ej in t'a a b'eyb'al.
Ak' nachajel wuuj yic wach' tzin k'anab'ajej a checnab'il. In gana tzin naub'tanhej juntzanh tas ix a k'ulej to satub'tac yochi.
Ay in och t'a cusk'olal, tek'an tzin utej in k'ana' icha yaj alankani.
Ochanh wed'oc yic wach' max wesej, tzak'an a wach'k'olal t'ayin yuj a k'ayb'ub'al.
Toxo ix wak'och t'a in k'ool to yelnhej tas ol wala', tzin nib'ej a ley.
Mamin Jehová, te naan in kachnab'il ix ak'a', manh in a cha q'uixwoc.
Van wak'an wip in k'anab'ajan a checnab'il yujto wan ak'an in pensar. HE
Mamin Jehová, k'ayb'ej in t'a a ley, in gana tzin k'anab'ajej masanto t'a slajwub'.
Ak' nachajel wuuj yic wach' ol in k'anab'ajej a k'ayb'ub'al. D'a wal smasanil in k'ool in gana tzin k'anab'ajej a k'ayb'ub'al chi'.
Cuchb'ej in t'a sb'eal a checnab'il, yujto ay in tzalajk'olal t'ay.
Ak' in nib'ejoch in kachnab'il tzak'a, mokab' b'eyumal tzin nib'ejochi.
Manh a cha wak'och in pensar t'a juntzanh yechel comon Dios. Ak' in k 'inal, yic wach' swak'och a k'ayb'ub'al t'a in k'ool.
Hak'uelk'och t'ayin a in a chekab' in tik, juntzanh tas alb'ilkan uuj t'a heb' ay elk'och t'a yol sat.
Te wach' a ley t'a yol in sat, yuj chi' colinel t'a juntzanh lolonel stzuntzancot yowal in k'ool, to tzin xiv t'ay.
Te xajanab'il a checnab'il wuuj, ak' in k 'inal, yujto tojol ach toni. VAW
Mamin Jehová, ak' a wach'k'olal yet' a colwal t'ayin, ichataxon alani.
Icha chi' ol yal in pactzitan heb' tzin tzuntzani, yujto a a lolonel ayoch yipoc in k'ool.
Ochanh wed'oc yic swalel a lolonel te yel, yujto yipk'olal yaj a ley wuuj.
In gana tzin k'anab'ajej a k'ayb'ub'al, malajokab' b'ak'uinh swactejkani.
Junk'olal ol in ajoc, yujto swak'och a ley t'a in k'ool.
Ha t'a yichanh heb' winh rey ol walel a checnab'il, manh ol in q'uixwoclaj walani.
Te xajan a checnab'il wuuj, ay pax in tzalajk'olal yuj.
Tzin xajanej wal a checnab'il, in gana wal yaji. Tzin te naub'tanhej a ley chi'. ZAÍN
Nacot tas alnakkan t'ayin, a in a chekab' in tik, a a lolonel chi' ix wak'och yipoc in k'ool.
Ha lolonel chi' tz'ak'an sniwanil in k'ool ayic ilk'olal waji. Ha tas alnakkan chi', aton wan yak'an in k 'inal.
Ha heb' te ak'umtac, max yaktej heb' in stzuntzani, palta max wactejkanlaj a k'ayb'ub'al.
Mamin Jehová, tzin nacot juntzanh a ley aytax ek' t'a yichb’anel. Ha t'a juntzanh chi' swik' sniwanil in k'ool.
Ha heb' sk'ulan chukal, syactejkan a k'ayb'ub'al heb', yuj chi' ste cot wowal.
Ha a ley ix wak'och in b'itoc t'a sat lu'um tik, yujto ek'elb'anhej weq'ui.
Mamin Jehová, tzach in nacot t'ak'walil, in gana tzin k'anab'ajejnhej a k'ayb'ub'al.
Sja in tzalajk'olal yujto tzin k'anab'ajej a checnab'il chi'. CHET
Mamin Jehová, a achnhej tzach in nib'ej. Toxo ix wak' in ti' to tzin k'anab'ajej tas tzala'.
D'a wal smasanil in k'ool tzin na'a to swak' tzalajb'oc a k'ool. Ok'oc a k'ool t'ayin, ichataxon alankani.
Ix in b'eytzitej in b'eyb'al, ix in yamoch in k'anab'ajan in kachnab'il tzak'a'.
D'a elanhchamel swak' wip in k'anab'ajan a checnab'il.
Ha heb' sk'ulan chukal ix yak'em yaal heb' t'a wichanh, palta max b'atlaj a k'ayb'ub'al satk'olal wuuj.
Ha t'a chimilak'wal tzin k'e waan swak'an yuj diosal t'ayach yuj a ley, yujto tojol toni.
Wach' wak'an yet' heb' syak'em sb'a t'ayach yet' heb' sk'anab'ajan a checnab'il.
Mamin Jehová, niwan chequel a wach'k'olal t'a yol yib'anhk’inal tik, k'ayb'ej in t'a a ley. TET
Mamin Jehová, wach' ton ix utej a k'ool t'ayin a in a chekab' in tik, ichataxon alankani.
In gana tzin a k'ayb'ej t'a a jelanil yet' t'a tas scojtaquej, yujto a a checnab'il swak'och yipoc in k'ool.
Ayic manto och in yaelal, manh jantacoc b'aj ix in b'at t'a skal chukal, haxo ticnaik jun, tzin k'anab'ajej a lolonel.
Ha ach tik, te wach' ach, wach'nhej tas tza k'ulej. k'ayb'ej in t'a a b'eyb'al.
Ha heb' ak'umtac, syal lolonel heb' manh yeloc t'a in patic, a inxo jun, tzin k'anab'ajej a checnab'il t'a smasanil in k'ool.
Ix ixtaxel spensar heb' sk'ulan chukal, xal in jun, swak' tzalajb'oc in k'ool t'a a k'ayb'ub'al.
Te wach' ix in elk'ochi yujto ix och in yaelal. Ichaton wal chi' ix aj in k'ayb'an a b'eyb'al.
Ha a k'ayb'ub'al t'ayin ek'b'al yelk'och t'a yichanh k'een tzijtumal oro yet' k'een plata. YOD
Ha ach ton wal ix in a b'o'o. Ak' in jelanil yic wach' tzin k'ayb'ej a checnab'il.
Ha heb' ay elk'och t'a yol sat, tzalajokab' sk'ool heb' ayic tzin yilan heb' yujto a a lolonel ix wak'och yipoc in k'ool.
Mamin Jehová, wojtak to te tojol a ley. Ayic tzin ak'anoch t'a ilk'olal, ayton wal yuj, yuj chi' icha chi' tzutej.
Aokab' a wach'k'olal sniwanan in k'ool ichataxon alan t'ayin.
Ch'ox swach'il a k'ool t'ayin, tzak'an pax in k 'inal. Ay wal in tzalajk'olal yuj a k'ayb'ub'al.
Q'uixwokab'el heb' ak'umtac syutej sb'a, yujto tzin sb'aj heb' wach'chom malaj in mul t'a heb'. Ha inxo tik tzin naub'tanhej a checnab'il.
Ha heb' ay elk'och t'a sat, heb' ojtannac kachnab'il tzak'a', smolb'ejokab' sb'a heb' wed'oc.
Wach'okab'nhej yaj in pensar icha syal a ley, yic wach' malaj b'aj ol in q'uixwoc. CAF
Toxonhej nanon yek' in k'ool b'ak'uinh ol in a colo', palta a a lolonel swak'och yipoc in k'ool.
Van yixtax yol in sat yuj in maclani b'ak'uinh ol elk'och tas alnakkani. Tzin naan icha tik: ¿B'aq'uinh ol ach ja ak' sniwanil in k'ool? xin chi.
Wach'chom manhxalaj wopisio yujto icham inxo, palta max b'atlaj a ley satk'olal wuuj.
¿Jantacto tiempo ol wil a in a chekab' in tik? ¿B'aq'uinhto wal ol ak'och syaelal heb' ayoch ajk'olal t'ayin?
Ha heb' ak'umtac syutej sb'a, manh naanoc a k'ayb'ub'al yuj heb'. Toxo ix sjoy olan heb' yic tzin telwi t'ay yalan heb'.
Masanil a checnab'il, yelnhej syala'. Ochanh wed'oc, ina to malaj in mul, palta manh jantacoc heb' ayoch ajk'olal t'ayin.
Toxo ijan tzin cham yuj heb', palta max b'atlaj a checnab'il satk'olal wuuj.
Ak' in k 'inal, icha syal jantac a wach'k'olal, icha chi' ol in k'anab'ajej in kachnab'il ix ak'a'. LAMED
Mamin Jehová, a a lolonel max k'exmajlaj. Aynhejek' t'a masanil k 'inal t'a satcha’anh.
Ha ach tik, tz'elnhejk'och tas tzal t'a masanil tiempo. Ha ach a b'onac lum lum tik, yuj chi' anheja' yaj lu'um ticnaik.
Masanil tasi, anheja' yaji ichataxon yaj alannakkani, anhejtona' ha' wan a k'anan ticnaik.
Tato maj in tzalaj in naub'tanhan a k'ayb'ub'al, toxom ix in lajwiel yuj cusk'olal.
Malaj b'ak'uinh sb'atkan a checnab'il satk'olal wuuj. Ha yuj a lolonel tik ix ak' in k 'inal.
Colin yujto ic innhej toni, naannhej a checnab'il wuuj.
Ha heb' sk'ulan chukal, wan stanhwan heb' in lajwieli, palta a inxo jun, a wal a kachnab'il tzala', a tzin naub'tanhej.
Ix wila'' to malaj junok tas tz'ak'an wach'il, haxo a checnab'il, manhxo jantacoc swach'il. MEM
Te xajan a k'ayb'ub'al wuuj. Masanil tiempo tzin naub'tanhej.
Naannhej a checnab'il wuuj, yuj chi' yelxo wal jelan in t'a yichanh heb' ayoch ajk'olal t'ayin.
Ek'al in jelanil t'a yichanh masanil heb' in k'ayb'umal, yujto naannhej a k'ayb'ub'al wuuj.
Yelxo wal snachajel wuuj t'a yichanh heb' ichamtac winak, yujto tzin k'anab'ajej a checnab'il.
Max yal-laj in k'ol swak'och in b'ha t'a chuk b'eyb'al, yic wach' tzin k'anab'ajejnhej a lolonel.
Maj wik'el-laj in b'ha t'a a k'ayb'ub'al, yujto wan in a k'ayb'ani.
Ek'b'al schi'al a lolonel t'a yichanh schi'al nok' yal chab' swab'i.
Te ay in jelanil ix wik'elta t'a a checnab'il, yuj chi' tzin chaquel masanil chuk b'eyb'al. NUN
Ha a lolonel sch'oxan wach' b'eyb'al t'ayin ichato a tz'ak'an sakil k'inal t'a yol in b'e, ha' sch'oxan b'e t'ayin.
Ach in Diosal, ix wak' in ti' t'ayach, yuj chi' yowalil ol in k'anab'ajej. Ol in k'ayb'ej in b'ha t'a a ley to te tojol.
Mamin Jehová, yelxo wal ste kus in k'ool swab'i. Ak' in k 'inal ichataxon alani.
Mamin, cha in wach' lolonel swal t'ayach t'a smasanil in k'ool, tzin a k'ayb'an pax t'a a k'ayb'ub'al.
Junjun k'u sjawi tas ay smay t'a wib'anh, palta max b'atkanlaj a k'ayb'ub'al satk'olal wuuj.
Ha heb' sk'ulan chukal, syak'em in yaalil heb', palta max b'atlaj a checnab'il satk'olal wuuj.
Ha a lolonel ix al t'ayin, wicnhej yaj t'a masanil tiempo, yujto ha' tz'ak'an in tzalajk'olal.
Toxo ix wak' pensar to ol in k'anab'ajej a ley masanto t'a slajwub'. SAMEC
Tzin chaquel heb' anima chab' sat, palta tzin xajanej a k'ayb'ub'al.
Ha ach ton ay ach och wenhuloc yet' in colnab'iloc. Ha a lolonel ayoch yipoc in k'ool.
Elanhec t'a in tz'ey a ex tze k'ulej chukal, yujto in gana tzin k'anab'ajej schecnab'il in Diosal.
Mamin, ak' wip, ichataxon yaj alankani, yic aynhej in k 'inal. Manh ak' lajwoc tas ayoch yipoc in k'ool.
Ochanh wed'oc, yic ol in colchajoc. Ichato chi' ol in k'anab'ajan a ley.
Ix a tek'kanem heb' syik'el sb'ha t'a a ley, yujto a sjelanil heb' malaj yelk'ochi.
Icha wal k'alem, icha chi' yaj heb' sk'ulan chukal t'a yol a sat, yuj chi' tzin xajanej a lolonel.
Ha in niwanil tik, tz'ib'xi yuj in xivk'olal t'ayach, yujto te niwan yelk'och a ley t'ayin. 'AYIN
Ha wach'il yet' tojolal tzin b'eyb'alej. Manh in actejkan t'a yol sk'ab' heb' ayoch ajk'olal t'ayin.
Ochanh wilumaloc yuj in wach'iloc. Mokab' in yixtej heb' ak'umtac syutej sb'a.
Van yixtaxel yol in sat yuj in maclan a jawi yic tzul in a colani. Van in tanhwan in ik'anel t'a libre ichataxon alankani.
Wach' tzutej a k'ol t'ayin a in a chekab' in tik, icha jantac a wach'k'olal. k'ayb'ej in t'a a ley.
Ak' in jelanil a in a chekab' in tik. In gana swojtaquejel a kachnab'il tzala'.
Mamin Jehová, stiempoalxo ak'an syaelal heb' sk'ulan chukal, yujto ix spitej sb'a heb' t'a a k'ayb'ub'al.
Ek'b'al tzin nib'ej a checnab'il t'a yichanh k'een oro te wach',
yuj chi' tzin k'anab'ajejnhej a checnab'il chi', haxo pax masanil chuk b'eyb'al, tzin chakkaneli. PE
Satub'tac a kachnab'il, yuj wal chi' tzin k'anab'ajej t'ay.
Ayic tz'alchajel tas syalelk'och a lolonel, icha wal sakil k'inal yaj t'ayonh. Sk'ayb'aj heb' anima emnaquil yuj.
Tzin te nib'ej wal a checnab'il, icha wal snib'an ha ha' junok mach yuj taquinhtial.
Ilincoti, ok'oc wal a k'ol t'ayin icha wal tzutej a k'ol t'a heb' tzach xajanani.
Cuchb'ej in t'a a b'eyb'al, icha wal yalan a lolonel. Manh in a cha ak'joc ganar yuj chukal.
Colinel t'a heb' anima malaj yok'elk'olal. In gana tzin k'anab'ajej a checnab'il.
Tzalajokab' a k'ool wuj a in a chekab' in tik, tzin a k'ayb'anpax t'a a ley.
Tzin te oq'ui, yujto malaj yelk'och a k'ayb'ub'al t'a heb' wetanimail. TZADE
Mamin Jehová, tojol ach toni, wach'nhej yelk'och a ley.
Masanil a kachnab'il, tojol toni, yuj chi' syal kak'anoch t'a ko k'ool.
Te tacnac in k'ool yuj heb' ayoch ajk'olal t'ayin, yujto ix b'atkan a lolonel satk'olal yuj heb'.
Ha tas tzala' tz'elnhejk'ochi, yuj chi' tzin xajanej a in a chekab' in tik.
Emnaquil anima in, patikab'il in el yuj heb' wetanimail, palta max b'atkanlaj a checnab'il satk'olal wuuj.
Ha a tojolal malaj b'ak'uinh slajwi. Ha a k'ayb'ub'al yelnhej syala'.
Manhxo animaoc waj yuj cusk'olal yet' yaelal, haxo a checnab'il tz'ak'an in tzalajk'olal.
Ha a kachnab'il tojolnhej toni. Ak' ja in pensar yic wach' aynhej in k 'inal. COF
Mamin Jehová, t'a wal smasanil in k'ool tzin awaj t'ayach, tak'wej in, yujto in gana tzin k'anab'ajej a ley.
Ha t'ayach swal in b'a. Ochanh wed'oc yic wach' ol in k'anab'ajej a kachnab'il tzala'.
Ayic manto sacb'ilaj tzin k'e waan, tzin k'anan a colwal yujto swak'och a lolonel yipoc in k'ool.
Pitzan in tzek' ak'wal, tzin naub'tanhan tas alb'ilkan uuj.
Mamin Jehová, ab' tas swala' icha jantac a wach'k'olal. Ak' in k 'inal icha wal stojolal a b'eyb'al.
Ha heb' snaan yak'an chukal t'ayin, ayek' heb' t'a in lak'anil, palta najat yajkan heb' t'a a k'ayb'ub'al.
Ha achxo pax Mamin, te lak'an ayach eq'ui, yelton wal syal masanil a checnab'il.
Pecatax ix wojtaquejel yuj a kachnab'il tik, a ach ix ak'kan t'a junelnhej. REX
Mamin, ilincot yet' in yaelal tik, tzin a colani yujto max b'atkan a k'ayb'ub'al satk'olal wuuj.
Colinel t'a yol sk'ab' heb' tz'esanoch t'a wib'anh. Ak' in k 'inal ichataxon alani.
Ha heb' sk'ulan chukal, malaj yalan yic heb' t'a a colwal, yujto max sk'anab'ajejlaj a checnab'il heb'.
Mamin Jehová, te niwan tz'ok' a k'ool t'ayonh. Ak' in k 'inal icha wal a tojolal.
Manh jantacoc heb' ayoch ajk'olal t'ayin yet' heb' tzin ixtani, a inxo jun, max wik'el-laj in b'ha t'a a kachnab'il.
Tzin chaquel heb' tzek' yib'anh sk'ulan chukal, aton heb' max k'anab'ajan a lolonel.
Mamin Jehová, yelxo wal xajan a checnab'il wuuj. Ak' in k 'inal icha wal jantac a wach'k'olal.
Ha a lolonel te yel. Tojolton masanil a k'ayb'ub'al, malaj b'ak'uinh ol lajwoqueloc. SIN
Wach'chom malaj in mul, tzin spech b'eyek' heb' anima niwan yopisio, palta te niwan yelk'och a lolonel t'ayin.
Stzalaj in k'ool yuj tas alnakkani, icha junok mach te niwan sb'eyumal syik'a'.
Max yal-laj in k'ool naojk'e lolonel, ste takkanel in k'ool yuj, palta tzin xajanej a k'ayb'ub'al.
D'a junjun rato swalan wach' lolonel t'ayach, yujto tojol ton a ley.
Ha heb' xajanan a k'ayb'ub'al, junk'olalnhej yaj heb', malaj tas tz'ak'an telwoc heb'.
Mamin Jehová, wan in tanhwan in a colani, yujto wan in k'anab'ajan a checnab'il.
Van in k'anab'ajan a kachnab'il te xajan wuuj.
Van in k'anab'ajan a checnab'il yet' a kachnab'il. Ojtac masanil in b'eyb'al. TAV
Mamin Jehová, k'eokab'k'och wav t'a ichanh, ak' ja in pensar ichataxon yalan a lolonel.
Axo in lesal jun, k'eokab'k'och t'a ichanh, colineli, ichataxon yaj alankani.
Swal wach' lolonel t'ayach, yujto tzin a k'ayb'ej t'a a b'eyb'al.
Ol in b'itej junok b'it yuj tas alnakkani, yujto masanil a checnab'il tojol yaji.
Aynhejokab'cot b'akhan a k'ab' t'ayin yic tzin a colani, yujto tzin te nib'ej a checnab'il.
Mamin Jehová, snib'ej wal in k'ool to tzin a colo'. Ay in tzalajk'olal t'a a k'ayb'ub'al.
Tzin nib'ej to pitzaninnhej, yic wach' ol in b'itan t'ayach. Aokab' a tojolal tz'och wed'oc.
Ix in satb'at icha nok' kalnel sacleminac yajb'ati. Cotanh, say in ek' a in a chekab' in tik, yujto max b'atlaj a checnab'il satk'olal wuuj.
